purchases were measured short the first two months of 1989 and the 
overage for 1988 was 0023 of the total volume of crude oil handled 
and measured by the company 
this percentage is well within the range of overage 
percentages reflected in the reports of the states which compile 
that data cordes said overage reports from texas and louisiana 
for example show many other companies with higher percentages 
cordes said 
