<TEXT>
a team of forensic scientists plans to dig 
into a colorado grave and perhaps settle the centuryold questions 
surrounding alfred or is it alferd packer to wit who killed 
whom and who ate whom 
packer a gold prospector and union army veteran has stood 
accused in history of killing five fellow prospectors and eating 
