parliament approved changes recommended by nemeth that installed 
six new cabinet members expected to speed the pace of reform 
the move came a day after the policymaking central committee 
offered to negotiate democratic reforms with opposition groups 
similar talks have brought about a more democratic electoral system 
in poland and legalized solidarity there 
