<TEXT>
whenever lee williams sees a school bus he 
thinks of his wife and daughters and of one gnawing question that 
remains for him a year after their deaths shattered his life how 
do you put it back together 
joy williams 10yearold robin and 14yearold kristen were 
among the 24 children and three adults killed a year ago sunday 
when an allegedly drunken driver slammed into the bus carrying 67 
people home from a church outing 
