about 10 years ago suburban white lake was 
considered too thinly settled for a new k mart 
now the prospect of future growth has prompted the nations 
secondlargest retailer to open a store in the area surrounded by 
meadows that developers plan to cover with homes 
this store will definitely be a store of the future with the 
